This paper involves the use of machine learning (ML) classifiers to predict post-cardiac arrest outcomes by leveraging high-dimensional patient data available early after admission to the intensive care unit (ICU). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
